Kier Pretax Profit Rises on Improved Construction Margins

-- B y   A n d r e w   N o e l
-- 
2011-09-15T06:06:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/kier-pretax-profit-rises-on-improved-construction-margins.html
Kier Group Plc (KIE) , a U.K. construction
company and homebuilder, reported a 24 percent increase in
adjusted pretax profit for the year through June, after
bolstering margins on building projects.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Noel at 
 anoel@bloomberg.net  